{
  "texts": [
    "• applying hyperparameter tuning on the training parameters (such as the learning rate).",
    "• using alternative transformer models (such as XLM or XLM-RoBERTa in the multilingual case).",
    "• using ensemble models (i.e.",
    "using the outputs of different NLP models and/or classifiers) to arrive at the final prediction.",
    "Finally, dimensionality reduction techniques could be used to reduce the length of the encodings."
  ]
}